Story: read the 'node install' help message
  As a cluster administrator
  I want to read help message of 'node install'
  So that I can understand how to install a node

  Scenario: node help list
    When I run ./node help install
    Then the help message should look like hoge\nfuga

usage: node install <node-name>

    -s, --script script file         The (Re-)boot scripts executed before installation

    -t, --trace                      Print out exception stack traces

    -h, --help                       Show this help message.
